, 68 ,70, 85]\n\nprint (bisect(l1, 47))\n\n# 3就係insertion point/index, 最終答案為3-1同3</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n當然自己寫binary search當練習下都好，呢啲基本功嚟。"},{"pid":"9a12f041c703750683d7b75dca575145a767ec6a","tid":2311650,"uid":90034,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"60f94d0f78d1d8046e1fc1259874fbe3d022182b","tid":2311650,"uid":51225,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"如果已經係sorted array，其實Python已有一個built-in module 解決類似問題︰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.python.org/3/library/bisect.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.python.org%2F3%2Flibrary%2Fbisect.html&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=99ebe373\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.python.org/3/library/bisect.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">from bisect import bisect\n\nl1 = [1, 17, 45, 68 ,70, 85]\n\nprint (bisect(l1, 47))\n\n# 3就係insertion point/index, 最終答案為3-1同3</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n當然自己寫binary search當練習下都好，呢啲基本功嚟。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T10:38:21.000Z","msg":"多謝指教，但係依個3只係表達左47插入去個list到將會係咩位置？ 但係好似岀唔到45 68依兩個answer啵。<br />\n<br />\n定係之後有得再處理個數據去攞到45 68依兩個數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d80cf512c99d64900b6fd7d628d2fad96737f8","tid":2311650,"uid":51225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a12f041c703750683d7b75dca575145a767ec6a","tid":2311650,"uid":90034,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"60f94d0f78d1d8046e1fc1259874fbe3d022182b","tid":2311650,"uid":51225,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"如果已經係sorted array，其實Python已有一個built-in module 解決類似問題︰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.python.org/3/library/bisect.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.python.org%2F3%2Flibrary%2Fbisect.html&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=99ebe373\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.python.org/3/library/bisect.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">from bisect import bisect\n\nl1 = [1, 17, 45, 68 ,70, 85]\n\nprint (bisect(l1, 47))\n\n# 3就係insertion point/index, 最終答案為3-1同3</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n當然自己寫binary search當練習下都好，呢啲基本功嚟。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T10:38:21.000Z","msg":"多謝指教，但係依個3只係表達左47插入去個list到將會係咩位置？ 但係好似岀唔到45 68依兩個answer啵。<br />\n<br />\n定係之後有得再處理個數據去攞到45 68依兩個數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T11:21:32.000Z","msg":"你咪用個index slice你原本個list囉，l1[3-1]同l1[3]"},{"pid":"11f4737eae09f80b6c9a4e7f8acf7e886ac59d84","tid":2311650,"uid":4288,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:10:46.000Z","msg":"#include&lt;iostream&gt;<br />\nusing namespace std;<br />\nint main(){<br />\n int n[] = {1, 3, 5, 7, 9, 11, 66, 499, 510, 999};<br />\n int const L = sizeof(n)/sizeof(n[0]);<br />\n int a = 6;<br />\n int c = 0;<br />\n for(int i = 0; i&lt;L; i++){<br />\n  if(n[i]&lt;a){<br />\n   c++;<br />\n  }<br />\n }<br />\n cout&lt;&lt;&quot;The number just smaller than a is &quot;&lt;&lt;n[c-1]&lt;&lt;&quot; and the number just larger than a is &quot;&lt;&lt;n[c];<br />\n return 0;<br />\n}<br />\n參考左睇唔透爸既做法 c++版本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6c23f5c6bb58d4b16998ec1999e04749e2fa92","tid":2311650,"uid":67527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7c1ea7e50b6baf5ac1e2872121c60490a588a4a4","tid":2311650,"uid":90034,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3212d5f8a3ae2d12b3c4152063c739248e544e06","tid":2311650,"uid":4526,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:35:54.000Z","msg":"Binary search"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:41:47.000Z","msg":"請問可以講多少少嘛。啱啱查左Binary Search似係搵list入面有冇依個值。好似岀唔到最近嘅值做answer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"